gnome-games 2.31.5
===================

Sudoku got a new hint system. In aisleriot the card are now slightly bigger. Also
build and GTK3 fixes.

Christian Persch (10):
      aisleriot: Increase card-slot-ratio
      build: Fix --with-gtk check
      build: Fix the librsvg .pc check
      aisleriot: gtk-3.0 build fixes
      build: Error out if clutter-gtk not found for aisleriot/clutter
      aisleriot: GSEAL fixes
      build: Fix clutter-gtk checks
      aisleriot: More GSEAL fixes
      build: Fix libcanberra-gtk check for gtk 3
      gnotravex: GSEAL fixes

Robert Ancell (3):
      quadrapassel: Rename 'bastard mode' to 'choose difficult blocks'
      gnotravex: Tidy up the code
      sudoku: Make hint suggest a square: Bug #616351

Xhacker Liu (1):
      Updated zh_CN translation.

